  - name: 
    text: I'm going to give you some tools this time. Pick them up.
    cooldown: 4
  - name: Anchor Bought
    text: Think of the Anchor as a tether to the ship.
    cooldown: 4
  - name: Grounder Bought
    text: The Grounder will ground you in the momentum of space. Whatever that means.
    cooldown: 4
  - name: Col4
    text: Use the Grounder to speed this up.
    cooldown: 4
